databaseQueries.query: SELECT `pokdakans`.`nama` as `nama_kelompok`, `alamat`, `jumlah_anggota`, `luas_lahan`, `pokdakans`.`updated_at`, `excerpt`, `total_omzet`, `no_hp`, `pokdakans`.`email`, `prestasi`, `longitude`, `latitude`, `photo`, `pokdakans`.`slug`, `status`, `kecamatans`.`nama` as `kecamatan_nama`, `categories`.`nama` as `category_nama`, `categories`.`slug` as `category_slug`, `users`.`name` as `nama_petugas`, `users`.`username`, `pokdakans`.`id` as `id_kelompok`, `ikans`.`nama` as `ikan_nama` FROM `kelompok_ikans` left join `pokdakans` on `kelompok_ikans`.`kelompok_id` = `pokdakans`.`id` left join `kecamatans` on `pokdakans`.`kecamatan_id` = `kecamatans`.`id` inner join `categories` on `pokdakans`.`category_id` = `categories`.`id` inner join `ikans` on `kelompok_ikans`.`ikan_id` = `ikans`.`id` left join `users` on `pokdakans`.`user_id` = `users`.`id` WHERE `pokdakans`.`status` = 'disetujui' and `ikans`.`slug` = 'patin' ORDER BY pokdakans.updated_at DESC LIMIT 1

SELECT `categories`.`nama` FROM `kelompok_kategoris` left join `categories` on `categories`.`id` = `kelompok_kategoris`.`kategori_id` left join `pokdakans` on `kelompok_kategoris`.`kelompok_id` = `pokdakans`.`id` WHERE `kelompok_id` = 39

SELECT `ikans`.`nama` as `ikan_nama`, `ikans`.`slug` as `ikan_slug` FROM `kelompok_ikans` left join `ikans` on `kelompok_ikans`.`ikan_id` = `ikans`.`id` left join `pokdakans` on `kelompok_ikans`.`kelompok_id` = `pokdakans`.`id` WHERE `kelompok_id` = 39
